  <section id="faq">
    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <p class="muted small">Empty at launch. Questions earn their place by being asked more than once.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="colophon">
    <h2>Colophon</h2>
    <p>
      The site is built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a> and
      hosted on <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com">Cloudflare Pages</a>.
      Content lives as markdown files in <a href="https://github.com/prerit-with-ai/preritkhanna">a public git repository</a>,
      validated at build time by Zod schemas. There is no CMS, no database,
      no analytics, no JavaScript on the page.
    </p>
    <p>
      Type is set in the system serif stack (Iowan Old Style on macOS,
      Palatino Linotype on Windows, Charter as fallback) at 17px with a
      1.6 line-height. Sans-serif uses the system UI stack. No web fonts
      are loaded. The accent color is a burnt sienna, used sparingly. Dark
      mode follows <code>prefers-color-scheme</code>.
    </p>
    <p>
      The site is designed to last decades. URLs are stable. Markdown is
      portable. If Astro disappears, the content moves to whatever's next
      with no rewriting.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

